---
title: Kiwi Chicken & Courgette Orecchiette with Rocket Salad
description: There are plenty of choices for a pasta feast out there, but we’re positive we have the winning combination of ingredients that will top the lot! Spiced chicken is combined with courgette in a tomato-based sauce for a hearty and warming meal which is sure to satisfy your tastebuds.
